    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款基于物理原理的混合在线/本地多人粘液对战游戏中，最多可有 8 名玩家同场竞技。目标很简单，吃食物变大，然后吃掉其他玩家。享受各种主题关卡、互动物理障碍和动态能力，每次都能创造独特的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/6c20a2ab9cd999b348fc0b33aaacd3d0.webp?t=1759238940\" width=616 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/604be47b3b01665d9266164b73c7e39a.poster.avif?t=1759238940\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/604be47b3b01665d9266164b73c7e39a.webm?t=1759238940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在竞技场上滑行、滑动和拍打，视觉效果超级令人满意，控制方式易学难精 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/b0c96acdd7db6790c89469e544c1fc76.webp?t=1759238940\" width=616 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/d2e7bfee7b636b1c83336dbeb1c5b06c.poster.avif?t=1759238940\" width=616 height=417 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/d2e7bfee7b636b1c83336dbeb1c5b06c.webm?t=1759238940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吃食物来成长！通过身体撞击粘液球，将其吸收，从可爱的小粘液成长为庞然大物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/5d1dfcad08c0635b0fcb14183bd659e5.webp?t=1759238940\" width=616 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/1f9a93feca1f5433a8b83188b1bb2980.poster.avif?t=1759238940\" width=616 height=123 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/1f9a93feca1f5433a8b83188b1bb2980.webm?t=1759238940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抓住并拖走食物，将其占为己有，但要小心！额外的重量会减慢你的速度，并可能成为你的累赘……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/2410bb1a57644969a39c3a3df19deb00.webp?t=1759238940\" width=616 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/5bca4b959bac47494d2c99549e50d096.poster.avif?t=1759238940\" width=616 height=147 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/5bca4b959bac47494d2c99549e50d096.webm?t=1759238940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据“粘液顺序”，比你大的都是危险的，比你小的都是食物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/95f09726d1d206814f32aabc564ff0a9.webp?t=1759238940\" width=616 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/ce7e8c0b195b6f64c023b5d21f38d9bd.poster.avif?t=1759238940\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/ce7e8c0b195b6f64c023b5d21f38d9bd.webm?t=1759238940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被吃掉的玩家会被困在体内，直到被解救或只剩最后一个粘液为止。</p>",
